{"answer":"Dev, ini masalah klasik. Kamu harus pakai **struktur 3 tahap** supaya percakapan nggak melantur dan calon mitra langsung paham siapa kamu:\n\n1. **Pembukaan (Ice Breaking & Izin Akses)** - Ucapkan salam hangat, tanya kegiatan yang lagi dikerjain, perkenalkan nama sambil tunjukin ID Card Amartha dengan jelas. Minta izin waktunya, \"Mohon maaf mengganggu Ibu, apakah boleh saya minta waktunya 10 menit untuk menjelaskan program kami?\"\n\n2. **Isi (Identifikasi Kebutuhan & Solusi)** - Pancing kebutuhan dasar mitra (tanya rencana usaha atau kendala modal). Jelaskan profil Amartha dan keunggulan komparatif, tanpa agunan, lebih cepat dari rentenir atau bank lain. Terangkan mekanisme kelompok tanggung renteng dan syarat dasar (KTP, persetujuan suami, KK).\n\n3. **Penutup (Call to Action)** - Tanya komitmen minat, minta tukar nomor WA, sepakati jadwal verifikasi, lalu tutup dengan salam dan terima kasih.\n\nYang bikin mereka curiga biasanya karena FO lupa step pertama, jangan langsung lempar produk tanpa izin dan jabat tangan dulu. Semakin jelas kamu tunjukin ID Card, semakin rendah kecurigaan mereka.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"81d37ada-8094-4b2c-8202-476875d219fc","document_id":"a7e3d8ca-957b-4a5a-91a2-e00a59741dff","source":"Komunikasi Dasar.md","title":"Komunikasi Dasar","chunk_index":0,"score":0.7307},{"chunk_id":"8970057d-7427-41e2-90a4-f966489abe74","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3543},{"chunk_id":"5a91aa72-484f-48b6-a934-8ce72d83d452","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3402},{"chunk_id":"5f0b9a1f-908d-4a9e-bd64-e06dbafb7f4e","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3019},{"chunk_id":"0a45829a-4110-408f-a35c-f0da4820e2c8","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.28},{"chunk_id":"6f8a0fb3-c7a8-4ab2-9826-adb499f9ff71","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2738},{"chunk_id":"6388d87d-c8c0-4fbc-ab79-98b63d8dab64","document_id":"1875771f-831e-40bd-9246-e24d284cf7ca","source":"Welcome to Amartha.md","title":"Welcome to Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2728},{"chunk_id":"7b758423-e757-4ef1-adf0-b75be87c8994","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2548},{"chunk_id":"d150e8a3-6a39-403f-ab54-6b8601b5ae8b","document_id":"a7e3d8ca-957b-4a5a-91a2-e00a59741dff","source":"Komunikasi Dasar.md","title":"Komunikasi Dasar","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"62e9cf37-2810-4b6d-b5b8-e05dcb46b83f","document_id":"a7e3d8ca-957b-4a5a-91a2-e00a59741dff","source":"Komunikasi Dasar.md","title":"Komunikasi Dasar","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"1c008037-ced7-4ab0-bcd7-f7b4612e50b8","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc1","resolved_query":null,"cached":false,"latency_ms":5327.31}
{"answer":"Oke, simak alurnya dari awal ya Dev. Setelah ibu-ibu setuju, prosesnya ikut tahapan *Sales Funnel* sampai jadi Mitra Aktif. Berikut langkah-langkahnya:\n\n1. **Sosialisasi** - Kamu kunjungi lokasi kumpul warga (Posyandu, Pengajian, Arisan) untuk jelasin produk. Tahap ini gerbang seleksi awal.\n2. **Komite Lapang (KL) & Onboarding** - Calon mitra diseleksi kualitasnya, dicek kemauan bayar sesuai kriteria RAC, plafond disesuaikan dengan perkembangan usaha, dan status pengajuan dipantau.\n3. **Pembentukan Majlis** - Tim BP merekrut kandidat Ketua Majlis yang dipercaya, komunikatif, dan bertanggung jawab. Ketua Majlis yang akan mengajak tetangga atau ibu-ibu dengan usaha yang saling kenal dan percaya (1 Majlis kurang lebih 15 orang).\n4. **Penilaian & Penetapan Limit** - Mitra tunggu penilaian kredit. Kamu pastikan mitra kooperatif, mudah dihubungi, dan data konsisten. Info limit akan muncul di AmarthaFin. **Tekankan ke mitra: limit tidak harus ditarik semua**.\n5. **Penarikan & Pencairan Modal** - Mitra ajukan penarikan sesuai kebutuhan dan kemampuan bayar. Dana ditransfer ke rekening terdaftar, tercatat otomatis di sistem.\n6. **Pembayaran & Disiplin Keuangan** - Angsuran dibayar via Poket (isi saldo lewat BRIVA, Alfamart, Indomaret, atau Agen AmarthaLink). Kamu dampingi 8 angsuran pertama, pastikan mitra paham jadwal, nominal, bukti bayar, dan sisa pinjaman. **Edukasi mitra untuk sisihkan 2-3x angsuran di Poket jauh-jauh hari sebelum jatuh tempo**.\n\n**Pihak yang terlibat:** Kamu sebagai BP, Ketua Majlis (penghubung kelompok), dan mitra anggota Majlis. Setelah cair, mitra masuk status **Mitra Aktif** dan target selanjutnya jadi **Mitra Berkembang**.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"7aebd9b5-97bf-4034-991d-b091ddf52bce","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":1.337},{"chunk_id":"7be39176-62a4-4065-9a3c-794f5150fc94","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":1.3123},{"chunk_id":"77291b7b-760a-454f-92e0-a79810d60caa","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.7739},{"chunk_id":"f6f5426b-a5da-4ae1-a1ae-0e349a0fccf3","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5751},{"chunk_id":"c388a3c0-57ad-4b75-8df0-feb599d9e2ad","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5508},{"chunk_id":"3517f93c-d33b-42f0-a795-2c4c101655dc","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.452},{"chunk_id":"30c17247-4a8a-4323-a951-eea0b96643e4","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4427},{"chunk_id":"9c6ddf57-f260-48dd-b78a-e1f99c58cacc","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3364},{"chunk_id":"55de3cfc-d995-4fc7-9af7-3a45bc28a369","document_id":"6cea8bbf-4a9d-45bd-b743-4b4cd81c1428","source":"Fraud Awareness.md","title":"Fraud Awareness","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3},{"chunk_id":"47fbdfec-f918-4f8a-9f36-0f989ceb608a","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2809},{"chunk_id":"d9732542-83b6-4dc6-aaa5-bfbd80bc0147","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Prod