{"answer":"Dev, gue paham banget perasaan lo. Briefing pagi tujuannya untuk menyelaraskan target hari itu, mantau capaian kemarin, dan nyusun strategi harian. Kalo cuma bacain data doang, ya sayang waktunya.\n\nBiar efektif, berikut urutannya yang wajib lo jalani:\n\n* **Buka dengan apresiasi dan doa bareng.** Sebelum bahas angka, sisipin apresiasi ke BP. Baru lanjut doa pagi sama pembacaan ayat suci.\n* **Review capaian dan penegasan target.** Paparin kekurangan disbursement, status PAR/NPL, dan target digitalisasi. Pake visual Papan Target & Achievement biar kelihatan jelas.\n* **Gali masalah per BP, bukan komando buta.** Minta BP yang belum 100% nyebutin rencana mereka: berapa UK, jumlah mitra eligible, dan sumber pencairan (dari GL, Modal, atau short tenor). Jangan diem aja, lo harus tawarin solusi.\n* **Bahasa digitalisasi dengan data.** Paparin update soal Aktivasi RF Poket, Investasi Celengan, Transaksi PPOB, dan Rekrutmen Agen AmarthaLink. Kalo lo belum bisa ngolah data digitalisasi sendiri, konsul ke AM dulu buat dapetin dukungan data.\n* **Komitmen verbal dari tiap BP.** Tiap BP wajib nyebutin jumlah mitra kelolaan (lancar & per bucket PAR), proyeksi komitmen (status BTC, rollback, stay, atau flow), sama target pencairan hari itu.\n* **Evaluasi, Q&A, dan closing.** Lo harus evaluasi komitmen mereka, kasi sesi tanya jawab, sampaikan update promo HO, lalu tutup dengan hamdalah dan yel-yel Amartha.\n\nIntinya, briefing pagi itu bukan seremoni. Lo harus bikin diskusi dua arah, pake data sebagai dasar, dan dorong BP saling bantu redistribusi potensi biar target point tercapai bareng.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"20221e7a-0d16-422a-adf2-ffbee4d876ab","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5937},{"chunk_id":"2c351da4-ce54-4d0c-8466-e9a68ceca293","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5903},{"chunk_id":"15b5a921-2ff5-4e7e-be60-ab084a0810ae","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5821},{"chunk_id":"fd151334-fb1c-40f9-aa88-9b82f4a49eff","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5764},{"chunk_id":"05452a41-a8d6-493f-bba6-650ca331705c","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4843},{"chunk_id":"0813099e-f813-4b37-8a91-10096b4cbc68","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4802},{"chunk_id":"5d52b8ae-dbaf-4794-9bc6-7530a71c2bf5","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4545},{"chunk_id":"5c2db8b1-c9ca-45af-a3ad-4e3e8c55a29e","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3915},{"chunk_id":"cee7e702-3bf0-4acc-bdd6-3f224a94474d","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"7c28cb3d-9eb6-43d8-821f-b72ae319ce59","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"4a93943e-efe8-4a6a-83e2-48a02e8f77d8","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"cc3e1b64-fb49-4ae3-a7d0-0041726c3fd3","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc3","resolved_query":"Saya Business Manager, briefing pagi saya tiap hari rasanya cuma seremonial. Business Partner pada ngantuk, saya bacain data, selesai. Padahal waktu berharga. Sebenernya briefing pagi tuh harus diisi apa aja sih biar efektif?","cached":false,"latency_ms":5542.0}
{"answer":"Penting banget, Dev. Agenda digitalisasi itu bagian dari akselerasi produk digital Amartha, jadi jangan diskip. Ada 4 fokus yang harus lo bahas tiap briefing:\n\n* **Aktivasi RF Poket.** Paparin update capaian aktivasi. Arahin BP buat prioritasin edukasi ke mitra usia 30-40 tahun yang literasi digitalnya lebih siap. Aturan mainnya: mitra WAJIB top up dan bayar cicilan secara mandiri, gak boleh dibantu BP.\n* **Investasi Celengan.** Cek capaian investasi. Prioritaskan mitra yang aplikasinya udah bersertifikat RF Poket, lalu sebarkan poster promo celengan ke grup WhatsApp majelis.\n* **Transaksi PPOB.** Minta BP simulasi perbandingan harga paket data/pulsa AmarthaFin yang lebih murah dibanding aplikasi pesaing ke mitra.\n* **Rekrutmen Agen AmarthaLink.** Ingatkan target 1 agen per majelis. Target utama: ketua majelis, mitra yang punya usaha warung/konter, atau mitra yang udah terbiasa pakai RF Poket.\n\nCoba minggu depan mulai sisipin satu dari empat fokus ini tiap hari, biar BP juga makin paham pentingnya digitalisasi.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"aa9c9260-ae1a-4ad2-bebe-f91aa7e9abea","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":1.9869},{"chunk_id":"1e8859c2-7984-4a81-869b-7d7580499d32","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":1.5584},{"chunk_id":"8c4608f1-d353-4403-988d-a9cb889e2809","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":1.4139},{"chunk_id":"3cca38ce-a8d1-4753-97f4-61beefb6c131","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":1.3084},{"chunk_id":"e4ea2a09-199f-49bd-9f9b-69f01008309e","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amar