{"answer":"Gue dapetnya di materi gak ada durasi waktu pasti yang disebutkan, Dev. Yang pasti ada ketentuan tegas: **briefing harus dimulai paling lambat pukul 08.00 waktu setempat**, dan BM diwajibkan memastikan **durasi waktu efisien** agar tim lapangan bisa segera bergerak.\n\nArtinya, balik ke lo sebagai BM. Panjang-pendeknya tergantung kedalaman bahasan agenda dan kedisiplinan lo megang waktu. Saran gue: ven…\n\nlo bisa cek langsung ke BM lain atau tanya Area Manager untuk patokan jam ideal di region lo.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"8de90985-9c2c-4969-be35-5ee4cf8f029a","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.6683},{"chunk_id":"2e1f5eb8-d95a-42df-ba44-0672a671d3bd","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5225},{"chunk_id":"8c764200-6466-4d44-bc21-e541abda79b3","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4249},{"chunk_id":"e4254c08-0bfd-41be-8d09-e46c291c6e48","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2977},{"chunk_id":"c01a9f98-732e-4798-8c29-5dab21751ab1","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.257},{"chunk_id":"f6f93cf1-0795-4371-afc4-32c4e2ebdbcf","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2014},{"chunk_id":"b0e24d44-0bfc-47e0-ab89-f0c81c859747","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.1835},{"chunk_id":"d8925474-f38c-4bff-85c0-5f4e450f8945","document