{"answer":"Dev, ini dilema yang sering banget terjadi. Jawaban singkatnya: kamu harus tegas pake data, bukan perasaan. Jelaskan ke BP bahwa **NPL** adalah indikator utama kesehatan portofolio yang menentukan arah kebijakan BM di Point dan bahan evaluasi kinerja BP itu sendiri. Rumusnya: %NPL = (OS DPD 90+ / OS Total) x 100%. Semakin tinggi NPL, semakin buruk portofolio kita.\n\nSampaikan langsung dengan cara ini:\n\n* **Pakai fakta historis.** Tanya ke BP: \"Rekam jejak mitra ini gimana di sistem? Kalau dulu sering telat di PAR, nggak eligible buat top-up.\" Ini sesuai filter kelayakan yang harus kita jalankan.\n* **Kasih analogi yang jelas.** Bilang ke BP, \"NPL itu kayak angka kematian di rumah sakit. Kalau kita terus kasih modal ke pasien yang udah kritis, rumah sakit kita yang dinilai jelek, bukan pasiennya.\"\n* **Fokus ke dampak kelompok.** Ingatkan BP, \"Satu mitra telat >90 hari nggak cuma nurunin skor kita berdua, tapi juga menodai reputasi Majlis dan SLIK internal. Modal ini tanggung jawab pribadi, tapi dampak kerusakannya berskala kelompok.\"\n\nKamu nggak perlu tough aja, tapi tegas berdasarkan prosedur. Edukasi risiko itu wujud tanggung jawab yang adil, bukan ancaman. Kalau mitra beneran berprestasi dan riwayatnya bersih, dorong lewat jalur cepat. Tapi kalau riwayatnya bermasalah, BP harus paham memperpanjang risiko itu nggak ada untungnya buat siapapun.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"888f7a1e-18b6-4b3a-923a-42e12044f07b","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5678},{"chunk_id":"1bf6cfcf-55b4-45a0-91ef-c369fd844623","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5296},{"chunk_id":"b5a4911d-eac3-4145-91ae-d5825b193369","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5165},{"chunk_id":"aefcd944-de1c-4549-a4a0-5aebc42e871b","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5141},{"chunk_id":"88b5a763-c783-4168-b958-da9b14796c84","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4541},{"chunk_id":"4dc778da-376c-466f-b6c1-5e86e58f3756","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4399},{"chunk_id":"57d296e5-c71a-4cc1-a7ce-23b7fb15e6cc","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4008},{"chunk_id":"4508298f-0323-4271-a8c7-4a4e2d7a8859","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3824},{"chunk_id":"4a8779f0-c8a3-4572-89d9-f6316b847bfb","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"ab791fb6-d5a0-4a34-b4c2-4bd1d42d851d","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"83a23895-ea2a-4a5c-851e-4bd7089697ed","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc4","resolved_query":"Kalo saya tolak, Business Partner saya ngotot karena mitra ini udah lama dan kasihan. Tapi kalo saya kasih, resiko Non-Performing Loan naik. Gimana cara saya ngejelasin ke Business Partner tanpa bikin dia sakit hati?","cached":false,"latency_ms":5106.43}
{"answer":"Nah, itu PR yang pas. Strateginya ada dua pendekatan sekaligus: **retensi mitra lanjutan** dan **akuisisi mitra baru** berkualitas. Jangan pilih satu, dua-duanya harus jalan bareng.\n\nUntuk mitra lanjutan yang udah ada:\n\n* **Filter eligibility dulu.** Kupas histori pembayaran di sistem. Mitra yang riwayatnya bersih, tanpa cacat telat, masukin ke daftar prioritas top-up.\n* **Kasih fast track approval.** Mitra kelas A ini harus diproses secepat kilat. Jangan dibikin lama, soalnya mereka adalah sumber pencairan paling aman.\n* **Pendekatan persuasif.** Buat mitra berprestasi yang mau istirahat, BP harus merayu. Yakinkan mereka sisa limit pinjamannya sayang dilewatkan dan bisa dipakai buat besarin etalase warung.\n\nUntuk akuisisi mitra baru, geser fokusnya dari kuantitas ke kualitas:\n\n* **Disiplin pipeline.** BP harus setor daftar calon mitra yang diupdate tiap minggu, bukan cari dadakan akhir bulan.\n* **Titik sosialisasi strategis.** Jangan asal keliling desa. Suruh BP penetrasi di titik kumpul potensial kayak Posyandu, sekolah (saat jam jemput), atau balai desa.\n* **Program referensi get member.** Latih BP buat bujuk mitra lancar yang udah ada biar merekomendasikan tetangga/saudara tepercaya buat gabung majelis.\n\nIntinya, kalau kamu cuma fokus ngejar mitra baru dan ninggalin mitra lama, kamu kehilangan setengah potensi disbursement. Keseimbangan ini yang bikin target operasionalmu stabil.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"33128c9c-3645-4e11-ba24-05cb2dd031cd","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4485},{"chunk_id":"7a0d1899-189b-4eea-9831-0a86d0166865","document_id":"fb449703-5859-4d68-a990-500f2081a643","source":"Basic Data Literacy.md","title":"Basic Data Literacy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4124},{"chunk_id":"dbe24604-5679-4497-9643-42660c4b9797","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3811},{"chunk_id":"e82990b3-2700-469f-8a16-a0cebb4d6b3a","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3509},{"chunk_id":"8dd4f4a4-3621-4d5a-ab98-7fa1ffca0a28","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3295},{"chunk_id":"ab273c7c-9775-40cf-a4dc-d5c2bbec31cf","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2911},{"chunk_id":"aac70ec4-5df6-44da-a4b6-e69f25aece1a","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2807},{"chunk_id":"a14ecb6c-2cd6-4427-8ee8-91961c3405a9","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2794},{"chunk_id":"0882d4e4-3faf-42b1-b61f-991b989b866a","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"7d4390c7-8686-4659-80f4-dc0f92b2b0da","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"fc8bf317-07b2-4418-8435-d9cb9d9ef22d","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc4","resolved_query":"strategi meningkatkan disbursement dari mitra berkualitas tanpa fokus pada mitra baru","cached":false,"latency_ms":6221.5}
