=== SCENARIO 7 ===
{"answer":"Dev, paham banget kekhawatiran kamu. Tenang dulu, di Amartha, aturan main penagihan itu sudah jelas berdasarkan kondisi mitra, bukan asal keras. Ada dua pendekatan resmi yang kita pakai:\n\n* **Pendekatan Berbasis Hubungan (Collector as Customer Service):** Dipakai untuk DPD 1-30 hari, mitra masih aktif usaha dan responsif. Alurnya: buka dengan ramah, dengerin keluhan (empati), tawarkan solusi seperti jadwal bayar bertahap, dan tutup dengan konfirmasi janji bayar.\n* **Pendekatan Konflik (Collector as Executor):** Diterapkan khusus untuk mitra dengan DPD tinggi (60+ hari), sering ingkar janji meskipun usaha berjalan (\"mampu tapi tidak mau\"), atau sudah berulang kali diingatkan. Baru di sini kita tegas dengan menyebut nominal dan konsekuensi.\n\nJadi kalau mitra yang kamu tagih masih DPD rendah atau menunjukkan itikad baik, pendekatan yang tepat seharusnya yang berbasis hubungan, ramah dan solutif. Coba cek lagi, mitra yang protes itu DPD-nya berapa hari? Karena prinsip kita adalah menjaga mitra tetap lancar, bukan bikin mereka takut.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"1916af32-4633-48b0-8faf-93c817d56b3d","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.675},{"chunk_id":"46464c29-ed1c-413a-a58a-939023845a02","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5804},{"chunk_id":"e757fa6f-3db2-4037-8637-33345fedf39e","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5374},{"chunk_id":"b9d48534-5eec-4ee7-821e-36ae4e3ff9b9","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5216},{"chunk_id":"a74dfd86-cd9c-4a02-8fe7-21fbc4f40a5a","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5207},{"chunk_id":"edaf0b94-4cac-4a1c-9db3-2f41b6f2d46f","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5125},{"chunk_id":"61e89cd2-7c35-4e85-9d49-f98eee389941","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5059},{"chunk_id":"b655610e-15bd-4f70-a4e0-e495637daca1","document_id":"6cea8bbf-4a9d-45bd-b743-4b4cd81c1428","source":"Fraud Awareness.md","title":"Fraud Awareness","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4863},{"chunk_id":"e4de5971-00a8-48b1-9a26-a69a7b86e4ee","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"a5999338-6b40-47b3-ba7d-b77723b6ff44","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"10f38316-557d-4c0c-a751-3d02383c8ce8","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"105acadd-b674-4f8a-803c-d1dcf05c2962","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc7","resolved_query":"Saya Business Partner, dapat laporan dari ketua majlis kalau ada mitra yang ngeluh saya dianggap terlalu keras pas nagih. Padahal saya cuma ngingetin aja. Saya jadi takut kena tegur Business Manager. Sebenernya aturan main tagih di Amartha itu kayak gimana?","cached":false,"latency_ms":5554.52}
{"answer":"Dev, ini penting banget. Amartha punya prinsip **Transparency** yang artinya mitra harus paham produk sejelas mungkin, tanpa ada yang ditutup-tutupi.\n\nYang wajib kamu sampaikan ke mitra sebelum akad adalah:\n\n* **Informasi produk dan rincian plafon** yang ditawarkan, dengan bahasa yang mudah dimengerti.\n* **Syarat dan ketentuan produk**, seperti besaran margin/bagi hasil, jadwal angsuran, dan jangka waktu pinjaman.\n\nJangan jawab sekenanya. Kalau ada yang kurang yakin, lebih baik bilang \"saya cek dulu, nanti saya kabari\" daripada memberi info yang salah. Soal biaya tersembunyi, prinsip **Responsible Pricing** menjamin Amartha tidak menetapkan biaya siluman di lapangan, contohnya tidak ada denda keterlambatan (pinalti finansial) untuk mitra yang menunggak. Jadi pastikan kamu sampaikan ini dengan benar ya.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"99fd1704-7a41-4af2-a22a-fa145f0abb72","document_id":"9adec8ae-ea93-417e-a2f7-20ad22417342","source":"Client Protection.md","title":"Client Protection","chunk_index":0,"score":0.9456},{"chunk_id":"3e668f94-8388-40c1-b54d-1b2bf7d5b1bb","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.7961},{"chunk_id":"1a1496dc-aa84-450b-989c-701c3f3c30d0","document_id":"f86fb8ba-7a3f-43e1-9e5c-231b289402ab","source":"Produk dan Layanan Ekosistem AmarthaFin.md","title":"Product Knowledge Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.7},{"chunk_id":"29937b7e-50d9-44b4-94a2-0470c6670c62","document_id":"9adec8ae-ea93-417e-a2f7-20ad22417342","source":"Client Protection.md","title":"Client Protection","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5408},{"chunk_id":"f9e85bc7-9389-4136-b962-3d90b0fa14a7","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5026},{"chunk_id":"716ee995-3d4b-4ddd-b33e-3ac824542543","document_id":"9adec8ae-ea93-417e-a2f7-20ad22417342","source":"Client Protection.md"