{"answer":"Satgas PPKS adalah tim yang dibentuk Amartha untuk menangani kasus pelecehan, tugasnya memastikan penanganan, perlindungan, dan pemulihan korban berjalan sesuai kebijakan yang berlaku.\n\nKalau kamu mengalami atau menyaksikan pelecehan, saluran pelaporannya:\n\n* **WhatsApp** ke Satgas PPKS di `+62 811-1001-7310`\n* **Email** ke People Care di `peoplecare@amartha.com`\n* **Atasan langsung / atasan dua tingkat di atasmu**\n* **Regional People Partner**: khusus untuk tim FO\n\nSetelah lapor, pelaku yang terbukti bersalah langsung di-PHK, dan kalau tidak terbukti, pelaku dan korban tetap dipisah lewat mutasi kerja. Korban juga berhak dapat layanan konsultasi psikologi dan pendampingan medis.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"cc2762ec-5d75-4cb1-b312-21720dd4ac97","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.7472},{"chunk_id":"4e1a5955-b95f-4f36-a673-f6966090e847","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.1902},{"chunk_id":"0293c631-1494-4456-a479-037a2bfee216","document_id":"6cea8bbf-4a9d-45bd-b743-4b4cd81c1428","source":"Fraud Awareness.md","title":"Fraud Awareness","chunk_index":0,"score":0.1016},{"chunk_id":"1fddc85d-9449-4d22-9523-3f857feec0c1","document_id":"6cea8bbf-4a9d-45bd-b743-4b4cd81c1428","source":"Fraud Awareness.md","title":"Fraud Awareness","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0608},{"chunk_id":"e1df4d16-9b4f-4a74-9fc4-03826d4a7c37","document_id":"6cea8bbf-4a9d-45bd-b743-4b4cd81c1428","source":"Fraud Awareness.md","title":"Fraud Awareness","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0543},{"chunk_id":"0704a2d9-e0b4-4058-af94-13264f5019d0","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0385},{"chunk_id":"a6c56d1d-15d1-4205-9fff-9bcd16722549","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0376},{"chunk_id":"9e252ba1-6909-4b06-8251-96a99d97bdea","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0288},{"chunk_id":"85b62d06-4928-4adf-9155-a115cc7c8635","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"d9600ac3-be09-4eef-9503-ea111b16051c","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc9","resolved_query":null,"cached":false,"latency_ms":3412.74}
{"answer":"Pertanyaan bagus. Kalau pelaku tidak terbukti bersalah, pelaku dan korban tetap dipisahkan melalui skema mutasi kerja, jadi tidak ada yang dibiarkan dalam situasi yang sama.\n\nSekarang soal kewajiban kamu sebagai pimpinan, berdasarkan SK Direksi ada beberapa hal yang harus kamu lakukan:\n\n* Membangun komitmen tim lewat pakta/piagam komitmen\n* Melakukan sosialisasi kode etik di unit terkecil tim kamu\n* Memberikan keteladanan dan pengawasan\n* Mengutamakan asas keadilan dalam penanganan\n* Bersikap responsif terhadap setiap pengaduan dugaan pelecehan\n\nIntinya, pencegahan dimulai dari kamu sebagai leader, pastikan tim paham batasan, ada ruang aman untuk bicara, dan kamu siap dengerin setiap laporan yang masuk.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"b50d7597-bdab-45c9-8b05-86885767c2aa","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":1.0},{"chunk_id":"86d48c0b-08f8-4415-8ba9-9728c0c21e54","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.7612},{"chunk_id":"0ca619d4-ddf7-406a-9332-59ab944827d3","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.7282},{"chunk_id":"7eb77ba9-9d20-4b03-94ef-bd92e86592f2","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.7269},{"chunk_id":"0e819cd8-4d58-4ffb-bb1c-b5d23503d8cd","document_id":"848eec2e-eaef-49e2-a875-eb2ab81233f6","source":"Anti-Harassment.md","title":"Anti-Harassment","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4988},{"chunk_id":"f83b867d-513a-4389-a794-07e8e3c8f593","document_id":"6cea8bbf-4a9d-45bd-b743-4b4cd81c1428","source":"Fraud Awareness.md","title":"Fraud Awareness","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3876},{"chunk_id":"f9515361-9cd5-4491-8db8-3ce2de37a535","document_id":"6cea8bbf-4a9d-45bd-b743-4b4cd81c1428","