{"answer":"Dev, pilihan tepat. Di Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving, setelah kita punya alternatif solusi dari 3 Ronde Diskusi, kamu perlu pakai **Action Matrix Diagram** buat milih prioritas.\n\nEvaluasi setiap solusi berdasarkan dua dimensi:\n* **Dampak:** seberapa besar pengaruhnya ke penyelesaian masalah.\n* **Usaha:** seberapa besar sumber daya yang dibutuhkan (waktu, tenaga, biaya).\n\nPrioritas utama adalah kuadran **Usaha Kecil - Dampak Besar** (Quick Win), misalnya monitoring harian atau penagihan door to door. Ini yang paling efisien.\n\nSolusi yang gampang tapi dampak kecil masuk ke kuadran **Usaha Kecil - Dampak Kecil** (opsional, nilai rendah). Kalau kamu sering ambil yang itu, coba latih diri buat nahan dulu dan cek: \"Apa ada opsi lain yang dampaknya gede tapi usahanya nggak jauh lebih besar?\"","sources":[{"chunk_id":"b192299d-c184-43d5-bd49-6143104fe66d","document_id":"993226a0-7b0b-4588-8b27-c3abe8531d55","source":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving.md","title":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5471},{"chunk_id":"3405e138-32c4-4dde-a047-c74c3b3aabbf","document_id":"993226a0-7b0b-4588-8b27-c3abe8531d55","source":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving.md","title":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3966},{"chunk_id":"a6095f56-11aa-4920-85d1-188e520b3a31","document_id":"993226a0-7b0b-4588-8b27-c3abe8531d55","source":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving.md","title":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2359},{"chunk_id":"04be445b-c5c9-4f82-afec-67af6ea8558e","document_id":"6718d6e9-fb52-43ad-9011-61cd8c05ad61","source":"Data Driven Strategy.md","title":"Data Driven Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2015},{"chunk_id":"68da24ae-fa9e-4289-9ab9-1d45e1bc6589","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0947},{"chunk_id":"db4202b0-c7d8-4242-b819-99bc83ba696d","document_id":"993226a0-7b0b-4588-8b27-c3abe8531d55","source":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving.md","title":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0778},{"chunk_id":"e1eb0867-b5f1-4734-8f27-b6cd6b33d7fd","document_id":"78b9f9df-2057-4944-be95-dd026d1052f8","source":"Basic Leadership.md","title":"Basic Leadership","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0712},{"chunk_id":"4b4334b3-9557-465f-ab8f-b5dfdd257f0b","document_id":"993226a0-7b0b-4588-8b27-c3abe8531d55","source":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving.md","title":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0597},{"chunk_id":"3329421c-5956-42c8-b6a1-88e44db0af49","document_id":"993226a0-7b0b-4588-8b27-c3abe8531d55","source":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving.md","title":"Framework Strategi dan Problem Solving","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc11","resolved_query":null,"cached":false,"latency_ms":4422.5}
