{"answer":"Dev, kalau BP kamu secara teknis paham produk tapi komunikasinya kaku dan mitra gak respect, kemungkinan besar yang kurang adalah **struktur komunikasi dasar saat bertemu calon mitra**. Bukan masalah pengetahuan, tapi cara menyampaikannya.\n\nDia perlu melatih **Struktur Tiga Tahap** waktu canvassing:\n\n* **Pembukaan:** Buka dengan salam hangat, obrolan ringan (tanyakan kegiatan yang sedang dilakukan), perkenalkan diri sambil tunjuk ID card, dan minta izin waktu. Jangan langsung 'jualan' produk.\n* **Isi:** Pancing dulu kebutuhan dasarnya (kendala modal/rencana usaha), baru jelaskan profil Amartha dan keunggulannya. Setelah itu baru masuk ke mekanisme pembiayaan dan syaratnya.\n* **Penutup:** Tarik kesimpulan, tanyakan komitmen, minta izin tukar nomor WA, sepakati jadwal verifikasi, lalu tutup dengan salam.\n\nSaran gue, coba dampingin langsung pas dia *canvassing* dan koreksi cara bukanya. Mungkin dia terlalu cepat ke teknis produk tanpa membangun *rapport* dulu. Itu biasanya bikin mitra merasa digurui, bukan dibantu.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"230e6ac3-7f79-43f8-acb9-b3c5aba1da27","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2956},{"chunk_id":"0da5e9ac-e185-4a0e-9120-c75ff1290f45","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2763},{"chunk_id":"b7d16ead-ef1f-457d-9d25-cf476c7c6b57","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2678},{"chunk_id":"17166e11-b971-4ded-a54f-c83a0b090d47","document_id":"a7e3d8ca-957b-4a5a-91a2-e00a59741dff","source":"Komunikasi Dasar.md","title":"Komunikasi Dasar","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2432},{"chunk_id":"b661e53f-c841-45ac-8a5f-893ac4441962","document_id":"78b9f9df-2057-4944-be95-dd026d1052f8","source":"Basic Leadership.md","title":"Basic Leadership","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2274},{"chunk_id":"254272c5-fa44-4e89-a03f-c0e5773a5f67","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.2271},{"chunk_id":"9c4d256c-8843-4b2f-bcbc-f8857ce91d7c","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.1984},{"chunk_id":"8a7aafdc-c75a-4a59-8745-47deab70529b","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.1833},{"chunk_id":"811ee21a-db17-40fd-89f0-fa1e44130f0f","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"8001ec41-4e36-4848-a82d-306feed73640","document_id":"78b9f9df-2057-4944-be95-dd026d1052f8","source":"Basic Leadership.md","title":"Basic Leadership","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc12","resolved_query":"Saya Business Manager, Business Partner baru saya pinter soal produk tapi kalo ngomong sama mitra kaku dan gak enak didenger. Mitra pada gak respect. Padahal secara teknis dia mampu. Kira-kira apa yang kurang dari dia?","cached":false,"latency_ms":5872.96}
{"answer":"Dev, itu masalah klasik, mitra baca pesan panjang langsung skip. Aturan WA-nya simpel: **maksimal 3 baris per pesan, bahasa daerah, tanpa istilah internal kayak 'KTA' atau 'approval'.**\n\nContoh **salah** (kaku & istilah internal):\n*\"Bu, terkait pengajuan KTA yang Bapak ajukan, saat ini masih dalam proses approval dari tim analis. Mohon ditunggu ya.\"*\n\nContoh **bener** (singkat & santai):\n*\"Bu, pengajuan ibu lagi diproses. Paling 2-3 hari kerja hasilnya. Nanti ibu saya kabari.\"*\n\nKalau info teknisnya panjang, kirim per bagian, jangan satu pesan panjang.","sources":[],"conversation_id":"test-sc12","resolved_query":null,"cached":false,"latency_ms":3400.73}
