{"answer":"Itu tandanya BP A kuat di sosialisasi dan rekrut awal, tapi lemah di kualitas profiling calon mitra. Drop di tahap cair biasanya karena data yang diajukan bermasalah saat dicek sistem (SLIK, underwriting), mirip kasus BP Yuni Shara di materi kita.\n\nAkarnya: BP A mengejar kuantitas tanpa seleksi ketat. PAR 1-7 juga perlu dicek, kalau tinggi, makin jelas profiling-nya asal-asalan.\n\nCoaching yang tepat:\n* **Perkuat tahap seleksi KL**: ajak BP A review standar kelayakan calon mitra sebelum masuk onboarding. Latih dia untuk screening lebih ketat, misalnya cek histori bayar, usaha yang jalan, dan domisili.\n* **Evaluasi data pengajuan**: minta BP A bandingkan sendiri data calon yang cair vs. yang ditolak, cari pola kenapa ditolak. Dari situ kamu bisa kasih feedback konkret per kasus.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"d978dd0d-233d-4f75-aa46-c6913830d996","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.8425},{"chunk_id":"62e9148b-cfbd-4580-811f-49fcc8c9ee5d","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.676},{"chunk_id":"3fed8922-4c40-454b-b0a3-7abd87c037cd","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5798},{"chunk_id":"4fd3895e-f44e-4d7d-9cd1-4b691cd28e91","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5416},{"chunk_id":"4b1c2358-f0ad-4bfc-85c2-b8065a3b6859","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.52},{"chunk_id":"608dbabb-155f-4da6-b957-5c5d7caeb0a8","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4791},{"chunk_id":"cabddd5f-e333-4c4b-9f28-4aba2c8d0f53","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4262},{"chunk_id":"d14debfd-afd3-4f7d-afd8-206cea36b641","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4179},{"chunk_id":"f424c797-223d-4d26-85f4-f1edb9fc5d1e","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"633ff5d0-db6f-4459-b1c7-adf29e6f040f","document_id":"c3e74aa1-a5cc-4f91-91c0-8730280a1877","source":"Sales Skill  Strategy.md","title":"Sales Skill & Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc14","resolved_query":"Saya udah analisa funnel Business Partner saya. Contoh kasus: Business Partner A konversi dari potensi ke onboarding bagus banget, tapi drop di tahap cair (cuma 30% yang approve). Ini diagnose-nya apa? Coaching yang tepat sambil apa?","cached":false,"latency_ms":4309.39}
{"answer":"Tiga pilar itu memang kunci operasional FO. Biar nggak telat intervensi, ini metrik yang wajib kamu pantau tiap hari dari dashboard:\n\n* **Pilar Growth:** Monitor realisasi *disburse* harian vs target, rasio mitra yang *reject*, dan identifikasi mitra *Drop Out* (DO) yang lolos SLIK dan punya riwayat PAR kecil.\n* **Pilar Recovery:** Prioritas utama adalah kecepatan turunnya *Forward Flow Rate* (FFR). Pantau DPD 1-7 (bucker ringan) dulu, baru yang berisiko pindah kelas. Contoh konkret: kalau mau tekan FFR 1-30 di bawah 2%, kamu harus hitung sisa OS yang harus dikejar.\n* **Pilar Digitalisasi:** Lihat persentase mitra aktif yang RF via Poket dan pemanfaatan Celengan. Pastikan mitra sudah top up dan bayar cicilan mandiri, bukan dibantu BP.","sources":[{"chunk_id":"b096b852-1ca2-475c-bb5e-6fe1ffc7801a","document_id":"6718d6e9-fb52-43ad-9011-61cd8c05ad61","source":"Data Driven Strategy.md","title":"Data Driven Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.799},{"chunk_id":"d4d4bf9a-f701-4e1e-ac75-0d9f6e77f554","document_id":"6718d6e9-fb52-43ad-9011-61cd8c05ad61","source":"Data Driven Strategy.md","title":"Data Driven Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5174},{"chunk_id":"c51a4e2a-3d03-4495-a856-416952558dc6","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.5018},{"chunk_id":"a3f4d783-7a8a-4c43-bca3-1445bdce4c70","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.4296},{"chunk_id":"bb5d7c01-4737-45c2-9b51-4bf7af3863a0","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3721},{"chunk_id":"a42a2c9f-9a6d-4129-b95a-b0f1bdd48c38","document_id":"1875771f-831e-40bd-9246-e24d284cf7ca","source":"Welcome to Amartha.md","title":"Welcome to Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3659},{"chunk_id":"e45c2b39-8f46-41d4-8668-45661ba09ac8","document_id":"b9c6943f-f2fa-4c66-a9bd-970b36cff073","source":"Business Process Amartha.md","title":"Business Process","chunk_index":0,"score":0.3556},{"chunk_id":"66f1cb5b-0a7b-4add-adff-f0b41aa5cfa9","document_id":"6718d6e9-fb52-43ad-9011-61cd8c05ad61","source":"Data Driven Strategy.md","title":"Data Driven Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.295},{"chunk_id":"83270b39-bf4e-4c30-8ceb-06bd52b49d40","document_id":"1875771f-831e-40bd-9246-e24d284cf7ca","source":"Welcome to Amartha.md","title":"Welcome to Amartha","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"b4aef7e5-b943-4a60-8b04-541e7352107c","document_id":"6718d6e9-fb52-43ad-9011-61cd8c05ad61","source":"Data Driven Strategy.md","title":"Data Driven Strategy","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0},{"chunk_id":"8e30de1c-36bd-4493-863e-f58bf719418a","document_id":"0735861d-46ab-43bd-be2b-767d24d6f42e","source":"Strategi Pencapaian Target.md","title":"Strategi Pencapaian Target","chunk_index":0,"score":0.0}],"conversation_id":"test-sc14","resolved_query":"Saya dengar ada target 3 pilar operasional di Amartha yaitu Growth, Recovery, dan Digitalisasi. Kira-kira dari dashboard, metrik apa yang harus saya monitor setiap hari agar tidak telat mengambil tindakan","cached":false,"latency_ms":5757.07}
